response.overview: Time to party! Amber and Daisy are dressed to impress, and on their way to the event that they have been looking forward to all week! But the travel will take a while and now, Amber needs to pee. They stop at the first place that they pass, which turns out to be a Gentlemen's Club. Of course, they can't stay away. They just HAVE to take a look inside, but they are not allowed, says the guy working there. Or rather... the extremely HOT guy working there.
response.tagline: What HappensIn The Club Stays In The Club
response.title: The Gents Club
